author: Sarah D.
title: Dem Rep. Jim McGovern’s plan to stick it to Trump tonight is ‘literally a tantrum’
text:
Dem Rep. Jim McGovern’s plan to stick it to Trump tonight is ‘literally a tantrum’ Posted at 5:35 pm on February 28, 2017 by Sarah D. Share on Facebook Share on Twitter 
If Democratic Rep. Eliot Engel thinks he’s teaching Trump a lesson tonight by refusing to shake his hand, he’s got nothing on his colleague Jim McGovern: "I'm gonna hold my breath til I pass out."— Dem Rep. Jim McGovern, on Trump's joint address tonight 
— Jennifer Bendery (@jbendery) February 28, 2017 Trending
